  "remarks": "Mother’s name: Fatima Muthanna Yahya. Photo available for inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice. Leader of Al-Qaida in the Arabian Peninsula (QDe.129) since Jun. 2015, pledged loyalty to Aiman al-Zawahiri (QDi.006). As of February 2020, reportedly killed in a counterterrorism operation in Yemen. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link: https://www.interpol.int/en/notice/search/un/4470245",
